title: Kordis Strong Tie Handle Swing Bin Bag Liners - 8 Rolls x 20 Bags. 50L White Plastic Bin Bags For Kitchen Bins & Large Indoor Trash Bin. 160 Heavy Duty, Unscented Garbage Bags - 60 x 90cm
features: SWING BIN LINERS: The Kordis Swing Bin Liners are the perfect food waste solution for any large kitchen and other household bins in your home. Each pack includes 8 rolls, and each roll consists of 20 liners, a total of 120 bags, working out at just 8.74 per liner! With our tie-handle swing bin liners, organisation and removal of your trash will be a breeze.

TIE HANDLES: These large bin liners are designed with simple tie handles, which are easy to lift and carry, and allows an efficient use. The thick handles are strong, ensuring no tears or split bags, aided by the heavy duty leak proof resistant base.

STRENGTH WITH LESS PLASTIC: Our 50 litre bin bags are made with high performance polythene, using less material to achieve the same strength and durability as other thicker products, saving on raw plastic materials, whilst remaining extra strong and light weight.
MULTIPURPOSE: These rubbish bags are ideal for a wide range of waste bins, including: food waste bins, kitchen bin, bathroom bin, office bin & any other large bins in your house.

SPECIFICATIONS: Bag measurements - 60 x 90cm. Capacity - 50 litres. Colour- White/Clear. Material - Polythene. Pack Size - 8 rolls of 20 bags, 160 count total. Kordis offer a wide range of waste disposal solutions, including - Pedal bin liners, swing bin liners, refuse sacks, food & freezer bags, and garden waste bags.
